### Arquivo de testes para API de Boletos
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api

### 1. Listar todos os boletos
GET {{baseUrl}}/Boleto
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Buscar boleto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/Boleto/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Buscar boletos por contrato
GET {{baseUrl}}/Boleto/contrato/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Criar novo boleto
POST {{baseUrl}}/Boleto
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contratoId": 1,
  "dueDate": "2024-02-15",
  "nominalValue": 1500.00,
  "clientNumber": "CONT-1",
  "finePercentage": 2.00,
  "fineQuantityDays": 1,
  "interestPercentage": 1.00,
  "deductionValue": 0.00,
  "writeOffQuantityDays": 30,
  "messages": [
    "Pagamento referente ao contrato de serviços",
    "Em caso de dúvidas, entre em contato"
  ],
  "pixKeyType": "EMAIL",
  "pixKey": "financeiro@arrighi.com.br",
  "discount": {
    "type": "VALOR_DATA_FIXA",
    "discountOne": {
      "value": 50.00,
      "limitDate": "2024-02-10"
    },
    "discountTwo": {
      "value": 25.00,
      "limitDate": "2024-02-13"
    }
  }
}

###

### 5. Criar boleto simples (valores mínimos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Boleto
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contratoId": 1,
  "dueDate": "2024-02-20",
  "nominalValue": 500.00
}

###

### 6. Sincronizar boleto com API Santander
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Boleto/1/sincronizar
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Dashboard de boletos
GET {{baseUrl}}/Boleto/dashboard
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Cancelar boleto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Boleto/1

###

